column2: SELECT top # p.modelMag_r, s.z, p.ObjID, e.EW_OIII_#, e.EW_NII_#, e.EW_Ha_#, e.EW_Hb_# FROM PhotoObj p JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID=p.objID JOIN emissionLinesPort e ON e.specObjID=s.specObjID WHERE   class = &&& AND  s.z BETWEEN # and # AND  s.z > # AND  p.modelMag_r BETWEEN # and # AND  e.EW_OIII_# ># AND  e.EW_NII_# ># AND  e.EW_Ha_# ># AND  e.EW_Hb_# >#
